data.description:
Don't miss this opportunity to own an ALL BRICK  home in the highly desirable, Dawson's Creek neighborhood, on almost .34 acre parcel. This immaculate Adams Home was just built in 2016. Some of the features of this home are:  *Two car attached garage plus ample additional parking. *Gourmet Kitchen with Stainless Steel appliances & plenty of storage. *Owners suite equipped with a double shower as well as dual vanities and a large walk-in closet. *Fans in all bedrooms. *Open living and dining room and a breakfast dining nook just off the kitchen. *A separate well and an Unrust Stain preventer for the irrigation system.  
*The sellers say they enjoy the quiet street and also watching deer roam in their back yard which connects to a Nature Preserve.
